    "raw": "Child of 21e3454c (local /healthz /logs /gpio /ir/ping).\n\n## Goal\n\nAdd GET (or POST) /dmz/ping on the office ESP32 debug HTTP server that does\nONE signed roundtrip to the DMZ sensors long-poll endpoint.\n\n## Behavior\n\n1. Build local state body (sensors fallback OK; include deployment config).\n2. Sign with Ed25519 (auth.toit / custom-envelope C service) using zone seed\n   from gitignored secrets generated at deploy.\n3. POST http://jovlinger.duckdns.org:5000/zone/office/sensors with\n   X-Zone-Signature, X-Zone-Timestamp, X-Zone-Name (long-poll hold is OK).\n4. Log what DMZ sends back (status + body snippet) into the onboard log ring\n   so GET /logs and the /dmz/ping JSON response surface it.\n\n## Notes\n\n- Encryption required (uses existing auth library already KAT-passing on device).\n- Direct local exercise: curl http://192.168.88.73:5000/dmz/ping\n- Parent already serves :5000 healthz/logs/gpio/ir/ping on thermo-esp32s3."
  },
